{"tid":242225,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[航拍撚] 想問下有咩機係可以裝自己部cam上去的？","createTime":"2017-05-13T18:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T15:41:54.000Z","uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1fd779dd54114e6ba67a8e2e41608513647ffa","tid":242225,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:08:37.000Z","msg":"新手未玩過航拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想平平地買部黎玩下 淘寶都得（更好）<br />\n但我見好多都係內置相機 而又像素唔高<br />\n我本身有部action cam<br />\n想問下係咪求其一部都可以裝部action cam上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/020646_c4dc795ccd7ed401ed523e5340e7bc5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F020646_c4dc795ccd7ed401ed523e5340e7bc5c.jpg&h=acd2ac67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38G053w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38G053w.jpg&h=8c11d374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://c.b0yp.com/h.6532im?cv=IUOEZudpzCu&amp;sm=0987d3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.b0yp.com%2Fh.6532im%3Fcv%3DIUOEZudpzCu%26sm%3D0987d3&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=37932105\" target=\"_blank\">http://c.b0yp.com/h.6532im?cv=IUOEZudpzCu&amp;sm=0987d3</a><br />\n<br />\n即係好似呢啲咁既機 可唔可以帶到部action cam 上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38a7bf14eb7f93346ea74b0699ce4cf94e732c1","tid":242225,"uid":100904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"波音747，速度快又穩定外國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0150e96b6f913f9a0d8693412ed8542890df7e62","tid":242225,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波音747，速度快又穩定外國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif